title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Norway - Heddal Stave Church
description:
In this video we will fly over the Heddal Stave Church. The Heddal Stave Church  is a parish church of the Church of Norway in Notodden Municipality in Vestfold og Telemark county, Norway. It is located in the village of Heddal. It is the church for the Heddal parish which is part of the Ã˜vre Telemark prosti (deanery) in the Diocese of Agder og Telemark. The wooden, triple nave stave church was built in a long church design around the year 1200 using plans drawn up by an unknown architect. The church seats about 180 people.
